    CSVWriter
    Class for the IO Management of the App (only access to external SD card not to internal memory) -create new empty .csv file -add line to file -check whether file exists or not -create new folders -check if SD card is mounted and writable
    MainActivity
    Activity called first when the app starts and call other activities
    PopUpNotification
    Helper class for showing and canceling pop up notifications.
    QuestionsActivity
    Activity to let the user make his input to the asked questions the answers will be stored in a .csv file on SD card
    TimeChooserActivity
    Activity to let the user choose four alarm times a day -one out of 9 to 12 o'clock -one out of 13 to 15 o'clock -one out of 16 to 19 o'clock -one out of 20 to 23 o'clock
    UserCodeActivity
    Activity to let the user input his usercode consisting of five letters an empty .csv file named as the usercode will be created on SD card
